<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="abcb-glossentry" ?><abcb-glossentry xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_2a818067-2778-48dd-bcc2-a630dcf39fd7" outputclass="abcb-glossentry"><glossterm id="_508aa3a2-b13e-4cb0-8204-f4313bc023a4">Smoke development rate</glossterm><glossdef outputclass="glossdef"><p>The development rate for smoke as determined by an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1175_0.13.0.xml#_52d35595-b475-460e-ac5e-5cd3e0a72e5f" id="_8f34a491-db66-440b-9365-e404718a7603" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Accredited Testing Laboratory</xref> testing flooring materials in accordance with AS ISO 9239.1.</p><callout id="_51bf0a4f-093e-489f-bc2f-c7f991fb1994"><callout-type ncc-info-type="notes"/><p>Until the adoption of the next edition of the NCC determination need not be undertaken by an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1175_0.13.0.xml#_52d35595-b475-460e-ac5e-5cd3e0a72e5f" id="_48fca8c2-2dc3-456e-b224-166e090df3d2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Accredited Testing Laboratory</xref>.</p></callout></glossdef><glossdef outputclass="glossdef-variation" variation="NSW" variation-type="REPLACE"><title id="_41c876f0-c727-476f-9ff3-5aa558f99f57">NSW REPLACE Definition</title><p>The development rate for smoke as determined by testing flooring materials in accordance with AS ISO 9239.1.</p></glossdef></abcb-glossentry>